title: Trillions Magazine July 2016 - Revolution or Evolution?
description:
Trillions is the business magazine with a reality bite. In the July issue, Trillions takes on the topic of a a new American revolution. Can American democracy be restored?

Includes exclusive interviews with foreign policy journalist William Blum, Rutherford Institute Director and attorney John Whitehead, Constitutional lawyer and Executive Director of the Center for Constitutional Rights, Vincent Warren.

What the Bill of Rights and the Universal Declaration of Human Rights means for you.

Hillary's Real Email Problem

Bexit - Be Careful What you Ask For

Revolution or Evolution?

And much more... 

Download previous PDF and audio issues for free at www.Trillions.biz
